Whatweb -- to check web server version and tons of infomration 
Weppalyzer - browser plugin to found all the version of the js, server, jquery etc. 
subbrute.py - for subdomain searching 
theHarvester - 
                  -d    domain to search
                  -l limit the result to work with 
                  -b data source (bing, google, linkedin, pgp, all, ...)
                  -f output to HTML or XML file 
     theharvester -d microsoft.com -b google -l 200 -f /root/Desktop/result.html   
Fierce          fierce --dns webapplicationurl.com  (to find Virtual host)         
SWFInvestigator - Flash assembling - Deassembling, SWF Tag Viewing, LSO (Local Shared Object) analysis, Dynamic Function calling.
xpath-blind-explorer, Xcat (https://github.com/orf/xcat)  -  Testing for XPath Injection 
